  "text": "For the further work it would be valuable to try the attack without the auxiliary trigger signal, however the time shift of the samples in this case is a nontrivial problem. There are some works describing an attack on misaligned samples [CITATION_1] , or trying to find the method which will help to align them [CITATION_2] .",
